               <orth>foghaintean</orth>
               <pron>[foĩntʹəṉ]</pron>
            </form>
            <def>[foĩntʹəṉ] Quotation: na foghaintean. Notes: wooden pins in warping frame.</def>
         </entry>
         <entry xml:id="Slips_LocheportPMacDonaldslips-idp165136208">
