               <orth>fuigheag</orth>
            </form>
            <def>Notes: piece cut off at the end of a tweed when taken out of the loom.</def>
         </entry>
         <entry xml:id="Slips_LocheportPMacDonaldslips-idp165137720">
            <form>
               <orth>glas</orth>
            </form>
            <def>Quotation: glas na caorach. Notes: the natural colour of the wool of the black sheep.</def>
         </entry>
